high_descs: Turn to the counter on your right.
Pick up the tomato on your right, near the pepper grinder.
Turn to your left and walk to the refrigerator on your left.
Put the tomato in the fridge, let the tomato chill for a few minutes then take it back out.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Put the tomato on the plate in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the white kitchen island.
Grab a tomato from the white kitchen island.
Turn left, walk across the room, turn left and walk towards the refrigerator.
Place the tomato in the bottom bin of the refrigerator, then remove the tomato from the bottom bin of the refrigerator.
Turn left and walk towards the microwave.
Place the tomato on the blue plate in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Microwave a tomato on the blue plate.

high_descs: walk over to the left side of the kitchen counters
grab a tomato off of the counter
put the tomato inside the fridge to cool it, then take it back out
put the tomato inside the microwave and close the microwave door
anns.task_desc: cool a tomato to put in the microwave
